cz.cvut.fel.matyapav.afandroid.components.types

Interface AbstractComponent

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AFComponent, AFForm, AFList, AFTable

    public interface AbstractComponent
    Interface for components. Defines methods which should be implemented by components. Some of methods like validate or send data won't be used by read only components (like AFList)
    Since:
    1.0.0.
